params.offset: The ID of the first bin to fetch data from.
params.pair: The Trader Joe pair to fetch bin data from.
params.size: The maximum number of bins to fetch data for.

returns.data: An array of BinData structs containing data about each bin.
returns.i: The bin id where data collection stopped. It is reset to 0 if end of bins was reached before collecting size bins.

getBins(address,uint24,uint24).notice: Fetches data about a range of bins in a given Trader Joe pair.

userdoc.notice: A helper contract for interacting with Trader Joe's liquidity pool pairs.
